text: Huang Meixia (born 16 November 1958) is a Chinese rower. She competed in the women's coxed four event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1958 births Category:Living people Category:Chinese female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of China Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
